<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Reset Password OTP</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 40px;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .otp-code {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      margin: 20px 0;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello,</h2>
    <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account associated with: <strong><%= email %></strong></p>

    <p>Please use the OTP below to reset your password:</p>

    <div class="otp-code">
      <%= otp %>
    </div>

    <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>5 minutes</strong>. If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <p>Thanks,<br />The <strong><%= app %></strong> Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= app %>. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
